        "created_at": "2019-03-26T20:47:18.655Z",
        "cooked": "<p>We\u2019re working on the issue related to <a href=\"https://github.com/apple/foundationdb/issues/53\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">memory storage engine recovery optimization</a> where you can selectively abort/skip the process if the cluster is healthy and then let this woker join the cluster as new.</p>\n<p>My questions are :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>how to reboot and delete data? I found the code to handle rebootRequest inside <a href=\"https://github.com/apple/foundationdb/blob/master/fdbserver/worker.actor.cpp#L777\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">worker.cpp</a>, but please_reboot_delete() is only thrown under the condition of <strong>g_network-&gt;isSimulated() == true</strong>\n</li>\n<li>Where is logic to deal with the please_reboot/please_reboot_delete exception ?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Thanks!</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 2,
        "updated_at": "2019-03-26T20:47:18.655Z",
        "reply_count": 0,
